  Description: You have elves, or possibly other aiuvarins, in your family tree.
    You have pointed ears and other telltale signs of elf heritage. You gain the
    elf trait, the aiuvarin trait, and low-light vision. In addition, when you gain
    an ancestry feat, you can choose from aiuvarin and elf feats in addition to those
    from your ancestry.
